{"tid":670373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記協斥公安局多項指控與事實不符","createTime":"2018-05-19T10:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T04:47:53.000Z","uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"296ea3e25c1b9d49d286a6111fd5d578c00ed9a5","tid":670373,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"北京公安局東城分局昨日發放Now 新聞台攝影師採訪時，被鎖上手銬帶走的片段。記協發聲明批評公安局多項指控與事實不符，表示極度不滿及強烈抗議，敦促內地當局追究施暴者法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n公安局昨日發片段指，事發時兩名男子不服從民警管理，抗拒警方執法。記協指公安局的片段經過刪剪，將公安的暴力行徑完全刪走，多項指控及聲稱與事實不符、混淆視聽。聲明指當時Now 新聞台攝影師徐駿銘已即時配合公安要求查驗證件，並無不服從管理，又指公安的行動與內地法規明顯不符，要求執法部門解釋對徐駿銘「叉頸」、按壓在地等強制帶離現場有何法理依據。<br />\n<br />\n記協又對行政長官林鄭月娥及其他官員的回應深表遺憾，認為政府呼籲記者遵守當地法規，同時對施暴者輕輕放下乃是非不分、本末倒置。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/527348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F527348&d=i4R458lrHm%2FInVyxz36gULIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=86b26b81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F527348&h=c0bbe00a\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/527348</a>"},{"pid":"a9eee60eccd026a6dacec181c8124d232f92583f","tid":670373,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://linepost.hk/images/1JACK/04/AE5003AB-6C79-427F-BF5D-29FE5DE66892.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinepost.hk%2Fimages%2F1JACK%2F04%2FAE5003AB-6C79-427F-BF5D-29FE5DE66892.jpeg&h=2b9e2638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88dd7360151afc3242683c1c67fe7f1a613c88db","tid":670373,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}